lbSetColor 
Behavior: local 
Game: Operation Flashpoint (1.5) 
Description: Sets the color of the item with the given index of the listbox or combobox 
 with id idc of the topmost user dialog to color. 
Colour is in format Color.  
Syntax:  
 lbSetColor  [idc, index, color] 
Parameters: 
[idc, index, color]: Array 
idc: Number of control 
index: Number 
color: Color 
Return Value: 
 Nothing